flowchart LR
    POLSRC[Policy Update Source] --> INGEST[Ingest & Segment]
    INGEST --> NLP[Normalize + Extract Criteria]
    NLP --> DIFF[Compare to prior Version]
    DIFF --> IMPACT[Impact Analysis on Rules/Prompts/Models]
    IMPACT --> REBUILD[Auto-Regenerate Rules/Prompts]
    REBUILD --> TEST[Regression & Safety Tests]
    TEST --> PUBLISH["Publish Policy-as-Code v(N+1)"]